## 0. High-Level Package Diagram

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class PresentationLayer {
        <<Package>>
        +UserAPI
        +PlaceAPI
        +ReviewAPI
        +AmenityAPI
    }

    class BusinessLogicLayer {
        <<Package>>
        +HBnBFacade <<Interface>>
        +UserModel
        +PlaceModel
        +ReviewModel
        +AmenityModel
    }

    class PersistenceLayer {
        <<Package>>
        +UserRepository
        +PlaceRepository
        +ReviewRepository
        +AmenityRepository
        +DatabaseContext
    }

    PresentationLayer --> BusinessLogicLayer : Calls via HBnBFacade
    BusinessLogicLayer --> PersistenceLayer : Performs Database Operations
```
